  "text": "Oxygen consumption. Oxygen consumption was measured in treated and untreated intact cells (2-3 × 10 6 ) using a Clark-type oxygen electrode (Hansatech, Norfolk, UK) in 1 ml DMEM lacking glucose and supplemented with 10% sodium pyruvate, as described previously [CITATION_1] .",
